            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glEnable</span></span>,
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glPolygonOffset</span></span>
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4775300"></a><h2>COPYRIGHT</h2><p>
